{
  "stem": "3277.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because he was very-- very-- he felt very bad in Stockholm that he accomplished, and I was left in Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That guy-- the diplomat?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the one who wound up in Stockholm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, his name?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yakov Babad, the friend.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this guy was-- the diplomat-- he was very happy, because he knew right away if I said Yakov Babad, I recognized his handwriting.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, you know, it's not so easy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't promise you anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He want-- he came to the consulate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He begged me for help.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He felt very uncomfortable that he is in-- in Sweden, and I am still in Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But this guy-- that-- don't lose, don't lose any-- any hope.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We will do something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, you know, he said-- you know, people like me, got refuse-- the government refused them to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said to me-- he-- first of all, he gave me money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said to me, first of all, don't say to anybody that you're meeting me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because to me, nothing will happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I can be persona non grata.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they will tell me, leave-- leave Poland and go back to your-- to your country.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But you-- you will go into the prison, and you'll never came out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And be very careful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we will meet each other very often.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But all the time, look all around that nobody is after you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And after a few times, he said to me, you know, Mark, give me all the names of those people who wanted to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Give me their names and addresses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I gave him the addresses.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
